node.text: Pretty cool but cooler w us

Want to automate your business but not sure where to start?

AI automation can save you hours of work, but knowing what to automate (and which tools to use) can be overwhelming.

Take the guesswork out!
Fill out a quick form and get a custom breakdown of the best AI automations for your business.

✅ Discover time-saving automations
✅ Find the right tools for your needs
✅ Start streamlining your workflow today

🔗 Link in bio to find out!

#makedotcom #automation #openai #aiautomation #ai #zapier #n8n #aiagents #gpt #deepseek
@jakeviza_ make could get there, although it would be much more complex than n8n
@promptible_ cool. I’ll have to check out n8n
Could make.com get there or is this flow too complicated ?
That's not langflow or n8n, right?
Please can u come to youtube
@lplavoie depends. Some cases, n8n and make have limitations. Once you hit those it’s beneficial to use code if you can. Although, in most cases make and n8n are able to get the job done.
Is n8n great if you are a developer? I got recommended using n8n and make sometimes over pure code automation
@promptible_ no hate at all I think what your doing is awesome but I just am saying ai is moving too fast and I saw the demo on gtp5 and so I just wanted to say that
@jayfromarizona what do you mean? Where did you saw that?
In comes chatgtp5 that does all these 😂
Pretty cool but cooler w us
That automation looks sick, have you thought of pairing it up with an automatic outreach system? Like the one I have...the level of personalization would be so good
Lmao monetizing Perplexity’s Deep Research didn’t even take 24 hrs 💀
